{"id":9037,"date":"2024-04-05T16:06:21","date_gmt":"2024-04-05T20:06:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=9037"},"modified":"2025-08-27T13:10:57","modified_gmt":"2025-08-27T17:10:57","slug":"caroline-perron","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/caroline-perron\/","title":{"rendered":"Caroline Perron"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Caroline est titulaire d\u2019un baccalaur\u00e9at en arts visuels de l\u2019Universit\u00e9 du Qu\u00e9bec \u00e0 Montr\u00e9al.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">R\u00e9cipiendaire de la bourse du gouverneur g\u00e9n\u00e9ral du Canada afin d\u2019obtenir un certificat en langue seconde de l\u2019Universit\u00e9 Bishop\u2019s.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Apr\u00e8s avoir travaill\u00e9 10\u00a0ans comme illustratrice pigiste, elle poursuivit son aventure au sein du CSS de Laval en tant qu\u2019enseignante en arts plastiques au primaire. Ces ann\u00e9es \u00e0 \u0153uvrer dans le monde de l\u2019\u00e9ducation lui auront donn\u00e9 l\u2019opportunit\u00e9 de travailler aupr\u00e8s de diff\u00e9rents groupes d\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ves.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Que ce soit en classe r\u00e9guli\u00e8re, SE, SL, SA, TSA son objectif \u00e9tait claire, favoriser l\u2019engagement de ses \u00e9l\u00e8ves. En tant que technicienne en travaux pratiques au d\u00e9partement de technique en \u00e9ducation sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9e, son intention restera la m\u00eame. Appuyer les enseignants du programme et optimiser l\u2019engagement de leurs \u00e9tudiants.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":9038,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[205],"departement-equipe":[280],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-9037","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-tech-en-travaux-pratiques","departement-equipe-education-specialisee"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/9037","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9038"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9037"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=9037"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=9037"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=9037"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=9037"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}